            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>點序(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6485:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6485\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6485-TW</a>)14日11:45上漲10.5元，股價漲停報116.0元，委買3,611,000張，成交11,553張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為NAND Flash Controller IC研發製造。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>點序(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6485:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6485\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6485-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲13.69%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲2.29%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+1,845 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+1,736 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+109 張</li> <li>融資增減：+1,494 張</li> <li>融券增減：+79 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
